                    <span>My husband is from Ireland and his best friend gave me this wonderful book.  We have a large family and the time for a decent prayer life can be limited.  It is an easy and beautiful way to bring prayer structure and guidance into a busy person's life.  It is a well worn book in my home.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A wonderful prayer book!  (high quality materials, too)</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
